ApproxsimClient.evolver
Class EvaluationsMatrix

java.lang.Object
  ApproxsimClient.evolver.EvaluationsMatrix

public class EvaluationsMatrix
extends Object

EvaluationsMatrix is a convinience class that by listening to an evolver keeps a double matrix updated with the numeric parameters of the evaluations produced by the evolver.
